    "seed:tree:MapReduce"],
   :weaknesses
   [{:trait
     "extraction prompts that ask 'pull out the important parts' without a typed schema produce inconsistent shape across runs — downstream :reads fail silently or get garbage",
     :avoid-when
     "downstream stages bind specific field names from the extraction output",
     :recommended-alternative
